rry-styles-penis-hit-by-flying-object-during-chicago-concert-3330933">Harry Styles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-nas-x-pauses-gig-after-fan-throws-sex-toy-on-stage-3464509">Lil Nas X</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-hits-out-at-fan-for-throwing-book-at-his-head-onstage-3485633">Drake</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-throws-microphone-at-audience-member-who-chucked-drink-at-her-on-stage-3475213">Cardi B</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-stunned-as-fan-throws-mothers-ashes-onto-stage-at-bst-hyde-park-3461977">Pink</a> 。</p><p>最令人担忧的案例是，在纽约演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bebe-rexha-collapses-on-stage-after-being-struck-in-head-by-fans-phone-at-gig-3457928">期间，一名观众将手机扔到</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bebe-rexha">贝比·雷克萨 (Bebe Rehxa)</a>的脸上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bebe-rexha-attacker-reportedly-threw-phone-at-her-head-because-it-would-be-funny-3458236">，因为他认为这会“有趣”，导致她</a>需要缝针。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-beyonce-team-up-with-megan-thee-stallion-for-savage-remix-at-homecoming-renaissance-show-3503240">观看 Beyoncé 与 Megan Thee Stallion 在返校节“Renaissance”节目中合作的“Savage (Remix)”后的视频</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
